<p>About Echa:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Echa Schneider has been working in local government since 2009. She currently serves as Communications Program Manager for the City of Piedmont, CA and has led digital transformation initiatives at the City of Berkeley and Oakland Public Library. Previously, she founded the award-winning hyperlocal news site <em>A Better Oakland</em>.</p>
